{
  "stem": "13874.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- Nothing was there to do it, and so it just fell on the wayside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that also is maybe typically of the fact that our father was dead, our mother gravitated more to her side of the family, and so relationship with our mother's family was much more intense than with our father's family.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually to all of them, I hated them equally, [CHUCKLES] most of them, at least.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because what was a fact of life was here we were, the poor little orphans, and everybody wanted to have a part in our education.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were pulled left and right and everything, and they-- whatever we did should have been done better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were regimented more than our cousins were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was at least-- it wasn't a pleasant childhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have a bar mitzvah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was traditional.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was kind of stilted, because two sides of the families met, and there was a little friction.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There always is friction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Primarily where there is inheritance, there is disagreement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the relatives of my father were-- had part of the business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when-- after he died, it was supposed to be split up, there were disagreements.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they carried through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Introverted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and mostly lonely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have much fun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- somehow I don't remember funny thing-- fun things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I read a lot, because I was introverted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My ambition was to become a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was quickly put aside after the Nazis came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have any friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being a twin, we were so interdependent on each other, that, at least I didn't need many outside friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had our old house.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
